TagLib version 0.02
===================

This connects Perl with Scott Wheeler's TagLib.  It's a good thing, because
TagLib handles all sorts of tags, not just MP3 ID3.

This is not even remotely finished.  It does work for grabbing basic tag
info as a hash reference, at least.  More to come...

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 TagLib 1.4

